# Vrinda Store Sales Dashboard – Excel Project

## Project Overview
This project focuses on analyzing Vrinda Store’s 2022 sales data using Microsoft Excel. The objective was to create an interactive dashboard that helps understand customer behavior, sales trends, and business performance.

## Objectives
- Compare Sales vs Orders
- Identify highest sales month
- Analyze men vs women purchasing behavior
- Monitor order status
- Analyze top-performing states and categories
- Build an interactive dashboard for business insights

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Pivot Charts
- Slicers
- Excel Formulas

## Tasks Performed
- Data Cleaning
- Data Processing
- Data Analysis
- Data Visualization
- Dashboard Design

## Dashboard Features
- Sales vs Orders Trend
- Gender-wise Sales Analysis
- Order Status Analysis
- Top 10 State-wise Sales
- Category-wise Sales
- Interactive Slicers

## Key Insights
- Women contributed 64% of total sales
- Maharashtra generated the highest revenue
- Delivered orders accounted for 92% of orders
- Set category generated maximum sales

## Outcome
The dashboard provides actionable business insights that can help improve sales strategy, customer targeting, and operational performance.

